longdesc=("cdparanoia is a Compact Disc Digital Audio (CDDA) extraction tool, commonly known on the net as a 'ripper'. It reads digital audio data from a Compact Disc and saves it to sound files. cdparanoia has been designed to read correct audio data even using cheap CD-ROM drives prone to misalignment, frame jitter and loss of streaming. cdparanoia will also read and repair data from CDs that have been damaged in some way.")

